
README for BIND 8-1 port for UnixWare 2.0x
------------------------------------------

This port is based on port for UW 2.1.2 by Larry Rosenman
(ler@lerami.lerctr.org)

This port was compiled and tested on UnixWare 2.03 using GNU C 2.7.2.1
It also can be compiled with native C compiler (default, not tested).
To install it just follow the instructions in src/INSTALL file.
To use GNU C do:

	make CC=gcc depend

after
	make ... links
	make clean

--------------------
